        <cdata>
          <text>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Reclaim Trade Powers Act&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This bill repeals the statute that directs the President to take certain actions, such as imposing a tariff of up to 15% for up to 150 days on articles imported into the United States, when necessary to address large and serious U.S. balance-of-payments deficits or certain other situations that present fundamental international payments problems.&lt;/p&gt;</text>
        </cdata>
      </summary>
